Package io.github.kinderhead.T2L.execution

Class Environment

java.lang.Object
io.github.kinderhead.T2L.execution.Environment
public class Environment extends Object
Global environment for current thread. Set the ENVIRONMENTS of a new thread's environment to this one's ENVIRONMENTS.
